history.content:
CS 189 does allow time conflict as per the berkeley course schedule

https://classes.berkeley.edu/content/2020-fall-compsci-189-001-lec-001

Does CS 189 allow time conflict in fall 2020? I have enrolled in one data science class DATA 144, which has the same class time as CS189. But it does not allow time conflict. I waitlist CS 189. Then I get an email notifying me that I am not able to enroll from the waitlist because of a time conflict with DATA 144. Is it because CS 189 does not allow time conflict?
history.subject: CS 189 time conflict issue
